                  </hi>. I am a carpenter, and work for Mr. Ramage. Here are two chisels belonging to me, which I lost above twelve months ago from the workshop-my name is stamped on them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18370612-name-926" type="witnessName">
